      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the mushrooms are cooking, trim, then slice your<strong> spring</strong> <strong>onion[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>lengthways until you have thin strips</p><p>Slice your <strong>cucumber</strong> into discs</p><p>Slice each individual <strong>cucumber</strong> <strong>disc</strong> into matchsticks</p>",
