    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate, large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Cut your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>brioche halves</strong>, cut-side down, and cook for 3 min or until toasted and charred, then set aside until serving</p>",
