    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mushrooms are cooked, transfer them to a clean board and shred them apart, using two forks – this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p><p>Return the <strong>pulled mushroom</strong> to the pan and mix it all up until fully coated in the sauce</p>",
