    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, spread the <strong>toasted brioche</strong> <strong>halves</strong> with <strong>chilli</strong> <strong>mayo</strong>, then load them up with the <strong>cucumber matchsticks</strong>, <strong>spring</strong> <strong>onion</strong> <strong>strips</strong>, <strong>pulled</strong> <strong>portobello mushroom</strong> and <strong>crispy</strong> <strong>onions</strong> – these are your<strong> pulled portobello mushroom burgers</strong></p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>fries</strong> with your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong> and serve them with any <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chilli mayo</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
